{"tid":537361,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)智能叛變 危機解密","createTime":"2018-01-22T15:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T18:39:09.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1a94bd0bbe171d6294e4dc05bcf963b68660e5","tid":537361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=b95sWr0rW4OL7IZFz0P7rL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=badeb1b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=b95sWr0rW4OL7IZFz0P7rL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2ce1fc2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3b/Movie_poster_i_robot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3b%2FMovie_poster_i_robot.jpg&h=e649866f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e5/Source_Code_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fe%2Fe5%2FSource_Code_Poster.jpg&h=80ce6935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在公元2035年，智慧型機器人已為人類廣泛使用。作為工具和夥伴，機器人在人類生活中占據了十分重要的位置，因為著名的機器人三定律的限制，人類對這些機器人充滿信任，它們中的很多甚至已經被視為一個家庭的重要成員..<br />\n<br />\n2.寇特&middot;史蒂文斯上尉（傑克&middot;葛倫霍飾）本是美國陸軍直昇機飛行員，某一日他發現自己變成了一個高中歷史教師蕭恩，與蕭恩曖昧中的女伴克莉絲汀娜&middot;華倫（蜜雪兒&middot;摩納漢飾）一同搭火車前往芝加哥，正當他感到丈八金剛摸不著頭緒的時候，火車爆炸了，他又回到一個軍事基地，接受柯琳&middot;古德溫上尉（薇拉&middot;法蜜嘉飾）的模擬測試，寇特被告知，他被五角大廈選中，進入了拉利奇博士（傑弗瑞&middot;萊特飾）發明的「原始碼系統」調查過去發生過的恐怖攻擊案件<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=b95sWr0rW4OL7IZFz0P7rL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5f0ffcbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=b95sWr0rW4OL7IZFz0P7rL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e9368606\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff23b441505b22f2f8008984df3375b2564ba62e","tid":537361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eabb31b40a1883e4dc34dee21b1c8580143b218","tid":537361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaa390423e8181fe783aad95624a49cb4e8ca61","tid":537361,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527f67fe01bf927c8b59c877a0d213c5023